query:

  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  oeeRecordId INT NOT NULL,
  lossCategoryId INT NOT NULL,

  quantity INT DEFAULT 0,
  description TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
